{"pageProps":{"data":{"leader":{"name":"陈雷教授","position":"讲座教授，信息枢纽院长","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/LeiChen.jpg","introduction":"陈雷，加拿大滑铁卢大学计算机博士，现为香港科技大学（广州）信息枢纽院长，数据科学与分析学域讲座教授，香港科技大学大数据研究所所长，香港科技大学教育部/ MSRA信息技术重点实验室主任。\n陈教授获得2020年中国电子学会科学技术一等奖，2015年ACM SIGMOD时间检测奖，2022 VLDB最佳研究论文奖，2014 VLDB优秀示范奖。陈教授曾担任VLDB 2019 PC联合主席。目前，陈教授是IEEE TKDE的主编，他是长江讲座教授，基金委海外杰青，IEEE Fellow & ACM Fellow，ACM杰出科学家，和VLDB基金会主席。","achievements":[]},"currentMembers":[{"name":"曹琛","position":"高级经理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/chen-cao.svg"},{"name":"陈昭","position":"高级经理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/zhao-chen.svg"},{"name":"李懋成","position":"博士后研究员","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/maocheng-li.svg"},{"name":"李林睿","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/linrui-li.svg"},{"name":"郭鹏宇","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/Pengyu_guo.jpeg"},{"name":"龙瀚林","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/hanlin_long.jpeg"},{"name":"黄飞瑜","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/feiyu.jpg"},{"name":"粟日","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/Ri_SU.jpeg"},{"name":"张成","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/cheng_zhang.jpeg"},{"name":"郭松岳","position":"博士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/songyue-guo.svg"},{"name":"顾佳乐","position":"研究助理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/jiale-gu.svg"},{"name":"王启正","position":"研究助理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/qizheng-wang.svg"},{"name":"崔凯","position":"研究助理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/kai-cui.svg"},{"name":"何思珝","position":"硕士研究生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/sixu-he.svg"},{"name":"王天愉","position":"医学交换生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/tianyu-wang.svg"},{"name":"米若玮","position":"医学交换生","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/ruowei-mi.svg"},{"name":"聂勇刚","position":"产品经理","avatar":"/static/website/images/people/yonggang-nie.svg"},{"name":"陈瑗","position":"项目经理","ava